msgstr "Membro dei Devil Killers"

msgctxt "908"
msgid "Talk_Smile"
msgstr "Talk_Smile"

msgctxt "60_Devil Killers Member"
msgid ""
"You that Suzuki guy? The taxi driver tryin' to take on the Devil Killers? Ya"
" cheeky fuck..."
msgstr ""
"Sei tu quel Suzuki? Il tassista che prova a sfidare i Devil Killers? Ma "
"guarda te che sfrontato figlio di puttana..."

msgctxt "72_Devil Killers Member"
msgid "It's 'bout time you learned to fear the Killers!"
msgstr "Era ora che imparassi a temere i Killers!"

msgctxt "96_Devil Killers Member"
msgid "No way... You're tougher than nails!"
msgstr "Non ci credo... Sei un osso duro!"
